9 Bxf6 
{This was the last chance to take on f6; otherwise after ...Nbd7 black takes back on f6 with the knight and keeps control over d5. }
9 ..Bxf6 
{Now black gets quite a good Svesnikov structure, so white has to play with a concrete plan, which is to put pressure on pawn d6. }
