19 c3 b5 (19 ..Bxd5 $6 20 exd5 Ne7 21 Nd2 exf4 22 gxf4 Ng6 23 Rdg1 Qe7 $1 24 Bd3 Qe3 25 Bxg6 Qxd2 26 Bc2 $1 {with a follow-up of Qf5, winning.}) 20 Nxf6+ Qxf6 21 Rxd6 Bg4 $1 22 Rxf6 Bxh5 23 Rxc6 Bxe2 {with the likely result being a draw.}) 
(19 Nxf6+ Qxf6 20 f5 Bxb3 21 axb3 Rfd8 {and black brings his king to safety on e7} )
