(24 ..Qc7 $2 25 Rxh6 Rc8 26 Bxf7+ Kf8 27 Rh8+ Ke7 28 Rxc8 Qxc8 29 Be6 Qe8 30 Qxe8+ Kxe8 31 bxc3 Nxc3+ 32 Kc2 Nxd1 33 Kxd1 $18 )
25 Rxh6 
